    <comment>- Removed some dependencies:
  * removed cava, it's not needed for AudioVisualizer on noctalia-shell anymore, can be installed as a standalone
  * removed dejavu-fonts and google-roboto-fonts, both aren't needed as a required packages, noctalia-shell uses system default font</comment>
